	If you do have any ideas, suggestions etc., send them to me at the
above address, fidonet 2:250/372.2 or tolawton@arcade.demon.co.uk. I will be
unavailable for the whole of August, but after that, new versions should
start pouring out.

	ARMs Race was compiled using RiscBasic, available from Silicon Vision.

